name: Irina Ishencko
description:
Hello!!! All for a good day. Looking for the man of her dreams. One with whom to be pleasant to be around all my life. Nice talking to you.
I am very kind, honest and sincere girl. it is possible that somebody would tell me that I’m a woman. since I’m already 30 years old. but I still feel as young as a 20 year old girl. With regard to the nature. I am calm girl. I can give advice, listen to people, understand it. For beloved man I am ready to fight with another woman. I want my man was just mine. when I find my beloved man, I will give him all my love, all warmth and tenderness, which is now kept in my heart.
